{"tid":933086,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《永續daddy》曼聯高層仍支持摩帥，沒發聲明是怕給摩帥壓力","createTime":"2018-12-08T09:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T10:38:26.000Z","uid":124292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d6b5efa951d2cf9f0eb5869832c933491fdd40","tid":933086,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"根據《曼徹斯特晚報》記者Samuel Luckhurst報道，曼聯在摩帥執教一事上的立場沒有改變。<br />\n<br />\n此前有傳媒稱，曼聯準備支付普捷天奴的4000萬鎊違約金，讓摩連奴被解雇，不過摩帥的經紀人文迪斯發表聲明否認了此事。<br />\n<br />\n根據《曼市晚報》的了解，曼聯高層仍支持著摩連奴，來自於高層的消息稱，曼聯專注於未來的比賽。曼聯方面沒有發表聲明，原因是他們擔心這可能會增加摩帥的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯目前在英超排名第8，落後榜首的曼城18分。摩帥在1月與曼聯續約至2020年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/man-utd-jose-mourinho-future-15522218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Fman-utd-jose-mourinho-future-15522218&d=1ddKXSppHI%2BY%2B54nan7uWpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=abd56533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/man-utd-jose-mourinho-future-15522218</a>"},{"pid":"05260e7efc8b00d680a7065671b04b6cc108e7f9","tid":933086,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4b2334727c164c600313228702f899a415a97e4","tid":933086,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"Free fall 曼"},{"pid":"b83b39442e60832a817ed2a475e9492bddf5e70d","tid":933086,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05260e7efc8b00d680a7065671b04b6cc108e7f9","tid":933086,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T09:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3aee20b1ffb81b21313b9c1ecc1c5964e9d549","tid":933086,"uid":12628,